window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Some forget why she was called the Queen Bitch. <i>Not anymore.</i></p> <p></p> <p>Bethany Anne is going stir crazy after more than a decade of having to be \"The Empress\". Now, her advisors have to deal with an Empress who is determined to be on the front line.</p> <p>The Ixtali's come to the Etheric Empire, hat in hand.</p> <p>Nathan decides that the best way to handle soft intelligence is to create a new company. What they <i>name</i> the new company should give a clue what it is about.</p> <p>The Skaine are able to finally get Ranger Tabitha's group right were their missiles can attack. The problem is, who is sucking whom into a trap?</p> <p></p> <p>Strap back in, because Bethany Anne is putting the Queen's crown back on.</p>"; 
